body_html:
The tensorflow is not compatible python version 3.6 , try installing it with version 3.5
Create the environment for tensorflow using anaconda using
conda create -n tensorflow python=3.5 anaconda

Try importing tensorflow after activating anaconda.
Hope it helps.
